{
  "chapter": 27,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十七回\"寒夜黑星\"。叶开来到十方竹林寺，与知客僧苦竹交谈，得知一位戴草帽的神秘白衣人借住禅房后，其余施主全部离开。苦竹带叶开查看白衣人房间——空无一物，只有两根钉子，白衣人夜间睡在绳子上，且以壁虎、毒蛇、蜈蚣为食。白衣人现身，自称只吃该死之人。叶开与其机智对谈，识破其并非冷酷之人。白衣人揭露身份——墨九星，青城山隐士，墨家子弟，脸上原有五颗星后增至九颗星，每颗星既是自我惩罚也是杀人利器。墨九星告知魔教四大天王中班察巴那已死于郭定之手，牒儿布亦被自己所杀（出示其护身符玉牌为证），剩余多尔甲和布达拉将在今夜现身十方竹林寺。墨九星在院中洒下银色粉末布阵，与叶开结为朋友。章末，短墙轰然破开，又一人施施然走入。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "我若早知道长安城里还有个这么幽静的地方，我也会住在这里的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "知道这地方的人好像是不太多。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "小寺的施主虽不多，也不太少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这七间禅房都是客房，本来并不是空的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "昨天晚上之前，还有几位施主住在这里，都是很风雅的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "现在呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在人都已到了大相国寺。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "他们都是昨天晚上走的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那位戴草帽的白施主一来，别的人就全都走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "是他赶走的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他并没有赶人走，可是他一来，别人就没法子再住下去。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我带你到他房里去看看，你就会明白的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就连我也一样住不下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "我不是苍蝇，也不是蜻蜒，总不能睡在一根钉子上。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这里有两根钉子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "两根钉子和一根钉子好像也没什么分别。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "有分别。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "我却看不出分别在哪里。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "但你却应该想得到的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "两根钉子，就可以挂条绳子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "绳子有什么用？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "绳子上可以挂衣服，也可以睡人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "那位戴草帽的白施主，晚上就睡在绳子上？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "而且是条很细的绳子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这屋子里本来不是空的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这里本来不但有桌有床，还有很多壁虎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "桌椅是他要搬出去的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "壁虎呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "壁虎全都被他吃了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "看来他的食量好像并不大，吃几条壁虎，居然就能吃饱了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "除了壁虎外，他当然还吃别的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "吃什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "住在这里的施主们，一到晚上，通常都很少出去走动。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为外面有蛇，毒蛇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "蛇也被他吃光了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "除了蛇之外，还有蜈蚣。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "原来他的食量并不小。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "所以我已经开始在担心一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "苦竹",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这里的壁虎和毒蛇若是全都被他吃光了，那时他吃什么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "你难道怕他吃你？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人有时我也吃，却很少吃和尚。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你是很少吃和尚？还是从来不吃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我通常只吃一种人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "哪种人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "该死的人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "这世上的确有种人就像毒蛇一样，你若不想被他吃掉，就要先把他吃下去。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "可是真正该死的人并不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "的确不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "那么你为什么不也像别人一样，吃些比较容易找到的东西。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你吃什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "我吃猪肉，也吃牛肉，尤其是红烧肉，小葱炒牛肉丝也不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "张三是个恶毒狡猾的小人，李四是个诚实刻苦的君子，这两人若是一定要你杀一个你杀谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "张三。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在你杀的却是李四。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "我已杀了李四？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "只可惜我连他的人在哪里都不知道。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你应该知道，他就在你肚子里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "毒的是蛇，不是牛，你杀的却是牛，杀了它后，还将它的尸骸葬在肚子里。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在你是不是已明白了我的意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你的话听来倒也不是完全没有道理。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这道理你从来没有听过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "我连想都没有想到过。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "看来你虽然不是诚实刻苦的君子，却也不是恶毒卑鄙的小人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你看得出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "就因为我看得出，所以你现在还活着。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你呢？你是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你看不出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你当然并不是真的姓白的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你是从青城来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "据说青城山里，有位高人，名字叫墨九星。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你知道的事好像还不少。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "虽然不太多，倒也不太少。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "只可惜应该知道的事，你反而不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你知不知道多尔甲是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你知不知道布达拉是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "看来我知道的事确实也不算多。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你想不想见见他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "我能见得到他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "只要你愿意在这里等，就一定能见得到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "就算要我等三天三夜，我也愿意。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你用不着等三天三夜，你来得正巧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "难道他们今天也会到这里来？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你既然愿意等，就不必多问，你若不愿等，也没有人留你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "和尚本不该多嘴的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "你这和尚说的话却太多。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ku_zhu",
      "text": "和尚不但要懂得应该在什么时候闭上嘴，也该懂得在什么时候闭上眼睛。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "看来他的确是个很懂事的和尚。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "真正不懂事的和尚只有一种。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "哪种？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "该死的和尚。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "从你眼里看来，天下的人好像一共只有两种。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "本来就只有两种，一种不该死，一种该死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "今天晚上要来的是哪种人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "该死的一种。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "今天晚上你是不是准备将这院子吃下去，所以先在上面洒点胡椒。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你的话说得太多。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你也笑得太多。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "那只因我已看出了一件事。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "我看得出你并不是个很冷酷的人，有时你心里也想笑一笑，只不过总是勉强忍住而已。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我为什么要勉强忍住？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "因为你想叫别人怕你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你还看出了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你若肯让我看看你的脸，我一定还可以看出很多事来的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你这是在自己惩罚自己？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "每个人都有罪。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你也不例外？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我也是人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你的罪是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我只恨不能杀尽这世上恶毒卑鄙的小人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "这并不能算是你的罪，你受的惩罚未免太重了些。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "若是遇见罪更重的人，这九颗星就是杀人的利器。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "杀人的利器？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你看不出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "我也连想都没有想到。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "能看到我这张脸的人本就不多，能活着的更少。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你脸上本来是不是只有五颗星。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "五颗星为什么变成了九颗星？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为世上的罪人越来越多，我的罪也越来越重。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "所以墨五星变成了墨九星。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在已没有墨五星，只有墨九星。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "这就难怪她会弄错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "她是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你猜不出？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "是不是上官小仙。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你也知道她？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你知道她是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这次我是来杀人的，杀三个人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "她也是其中之一？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "她本来是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "现在呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在我才发现，这世上比她更该死的人还有很多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "最该死的是哪几个？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "多尔甲和布达拉。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "要杀这两个人，只怕很不容易。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我本就没有打算活着回去。魔教中的四大天王，只要还有一个活在世上，我就绝不回青城。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "可是你就是杀了他们两个，也还有两个活着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "没有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "怎么会没有了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "班察巴那已死在郭定手里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "牒儿布呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这就是牒儿布的护身符，他活着的时候，总是随身带着的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "现在怎么会到了你身上？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为他已是个死人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "是你杀了他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你在哪里遇见他的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "长安城外。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "他也下了魔山？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他们的魔山本就在虚无缥缈间，他们的人在哪里，哪里就是他们的魔山。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "所以现在他们的魔山就在长安城？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他们的人若不死，九九八十一天之内，这长安城就要变成座魔城。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "魔城？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "魔教中也有两种人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "哪两种？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "一种是他们魔教的弟子，还有一种是死人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "幸好他们的秘密已被你发现了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "对我说来，这世上根本没有秘密。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "你知道的事确实不少。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "我只奇怪，你怎会知道这么多事的，你本是个不出山的隐士。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你错了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "墨家的精神并不是出世的，而是入世的，为了急人之难，墨家子弟一向不惜摩顶放踵，刀斧加身。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我也早就知道你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你姓叶，叫叶开。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "木叶的叶，开心的开。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你总是很开心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "因为我很少去想那些不开心事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "据说你的飞刀，现在可算是当世第一。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "我也听人这么样说过，所以我的麻烦也总是天下第一。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "总有一天我会知道的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "知道什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你的飞刀究竟是不是天下第一？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "你若真的想知道，我的麻烦就又多了一件。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你不想看看我的星究竟是不是能杀人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "我不想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "因为我们已经是朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你的朋友只怕太多了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "朋友多些，总比没有朋友好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "也许就因为你的朋友比别人多，所以麻烦也比别人多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "麻烦多些，也比没有麻烦好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "text": "因为真正没有麻烦的，也只有一种人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_jiu_xing",
      "speaker_name": "墨九星",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "死人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    }
  ],
